<div class="modalcontainer">
<div class="modalbox">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<h2><span>著作信息</span></h2>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit first">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/4" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style="height:2em;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
<p><br />
<strong>SCP-CN-1868</strong> - 自知之明</p>
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-zhengshi" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5288378); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5288378&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606781501" alt="Dr Zhengshi" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5288378)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-zhengshi" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5288378); return false;">Dr Zhengshi</a></span></p>
<hr />
